                    <li>Mentored junior developers and established code review best practices.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gray-800 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-400">Computer Science Degree</h2>
                <h3 class="text-gray-400 mb-4">University of Technology | 2018 - 2022</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-300">Graduated with honors. Specialized in data structures, algorithms, and full-stack web development.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-gray-800 text-center p-6 text-gray-500 text-sm">
        &copy; 2026 DevPortfolio. Built with NestJS & Tailwind.
    </footer>
